'''Grillage''' refers to large pieces of [[wood]], typically [[scrap]], that are used to make an object level with the ground. Typicall used by the military in bridging applications.

[[French language|French]], from [[Old French]], ''[[trellis]]'', from greille, ''[[gridiron]]''

